    dc:description "Fig. 14. Composite plate of Polhillia groenewaldii. 1 — Flower front view; 2 — Flower side view; 3 — Flower bottom view; 4 — Wing petals; 5 — Keel petals; 6 — Androecium; 7 — Gynoecium; 8 — Fruit; 9 — Close-up of leaves and stipules; 10 — Habit.Scale bars: 4 mm. Photographs by B.du Preez" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10496894/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10496876>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Map showing distribution of Polhillia in the Western Cape Province, South Africa.A — Distribution of extra Overberg species; B — Species within and just outside of the Overberg region. Note expansion of square in A to map in B." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10496876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

